com.intuit.wasabi.eventlog.events

Interface EventLogEvent

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ApplicationEvent, BucketEvent, ChangeEvent, CreateEvent, ExperimentEvent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractChangeEvent, AbstractEvent, AuthorizationChangeEvent, BucketChangeEvent, BucketCreateEvent, BucketDeleteEvent, ExperimentChangeEvent, ExperimentCreateEvent, SimpleEvent

    public interface EventLogEvent
    An EventLogEvent stores all data needed to identify an event:
    • the user
    • the date
    • possible additional fields
    An EventLogEvent is the base interface for all other Event interfaces.
